title: McMinn County High School vs. Soddy Daisy High School
text: Share Updated: 12:21 am Soddy Daisy, TN (WDEF) - Early in the 1st Quarter, Trojan QB Justin Cooke hands to RB Christian Bell for touchdown.Score is 7-0, Soddy Daisy. Bottom of 1st Quarter, Trojan TE Ty Boeck catches in end zone.Score is 14-0, Soddy on top.Early in the 2nd Quarter, it's McMinn's turn.QB Bradley Hayes hands to WR Dylan McCosh for a touchdown.Score is 14-7, Soddy Daisy.Trojan QB Justin Cooke throws to WR Tre Carter for the touchdown.Score is 20-7, Soddy Daisy.Bottom of the 2nd Quarter, Trojan QB Justin Cooke throws long to WR Jacob Lemons for the touchdown.Score is 26-7, Soddy Daisy.Final score is 42-21, Trojans win!!!
